data.Name: Babe Rainbow
data.Bio: North Coast cosmic conduits Babe Rainbow are at their laconic, luminous peak, curiously exploring their place in sonic space while permaculturally rooted here on Planet Earth, to drifting, dazzling effect. Sprouting from the high vibrational vortex that is Australia's Eastern-most tip - Byron Bay - the music of Babe Rainbow acts as an extension of the consciously living community that has made the area so magnetic for decades. Gently psychedelic and lightly jammy Read more on Last.fm
